285
0:12:14.76,000 --> 0:12:16,000
not just about GDP alone,

286
0:12:16.82,000 --> 0:12:18,000
but inclusive, sustainable growth

287
0:12:19.399,000 --> 0:12:23,000
that brings real improvements in people's lives.

